<div class="post_list_content_unit">
<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/nation-state-ukraine-hungary/" title="View full">Churchill and the Nation-State: Ukraine and Hungary Today</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">06</div>
<div class="date-m">Apr</div>
<div class="date-y">2022</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>ANDREW ROBERTS</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/nation-state-ukraine-hungary/" title="Read more about Churchill and the Nation-State: Ukraine and Hungary Today">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/1946May8Holland-770x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="nation-state" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/1946May8Holland-770x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="nation-state" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">Churchill was a powerful advocate of the nation-state. The EU is not one, but Ukraine has shown that it is. Day after day, in their streets and suburbs and forests, ordinary Ukrainians are showing that they believe it is a real country. They would not be fighting and dying if they did not believe this.</div>

<div class="post_list_cats">
<span class="post_list_cats_label">Posted in:</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/resources/churchill-and-europe-resources/">Churchill and Europe</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/resources/churchill-for-today-resources/">Churchill for Today</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/resources/">Resources</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
</div>

<div class="post_list_item_tags">
<span class="post_list_tags_label">Tags:</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/andrew-roberts/">Andrew Roberts</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/hungary/">Hungary</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/ukraine/">Ukraine</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/tag/winston-s-churchill/">Winston S. Churchill</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
</div>
<div class="post_list_btn_more">
