<div class="post_list_content_unit">
<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/willett-daylight-savings/" title="View full">Daylight Savings Time: A Silent Toast to William Willett</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">14</div>
<div class="date-m">Mar</div>
<div class="date-y">2021</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>WINSTON S. CHURCHILL</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/willett-daylight-savings/" title="Read more about Daylight Savings Time: A Silent Toast to William Willett">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="635" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DaylightInn-635x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Willett" decoding="async" /><noscript><img width="635" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/DaylightInn-635x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Willett" decoding="async" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">“Springing ahead” to Daylight Time, we recall Churchill’s support of Willett, whose “vision and driving power” led to this “great reform.”</div>

<div class="post_list_cats">
<span class="post_list_cats_label">Posted in:</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/resources/churchill-for-today-resources/">Churchill for Today</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/category/resources/">Resources</a><span class="post_list_divider">,</span>
</div>

