<div class="post_list_content_unit">
<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-whitehall/" title="View full">A Walking Tour of Winston Churchill&#8217;s Historic Whitehall</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">06</div>
<div class="date-m">Oct</div>
<div class="date-y">2020</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>THE CHURCHILL PROJECT</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/churchill-whitehall/" title="Read more about A Walking Tour of Winston Churchill&#8217;s Historic Whitehall">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/downing-street-770x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Whitehall" decoding="async" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/downing-street-770x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Whitehall" decoding="async" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">The Churchill Project provides descriptions of the twelve most significant locations in Whitehall, London as they relate to Winston Churchill. </div>

