<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/current-contentions/" title="View full">Churchill Contentions: “The Invasion of the Idiots”</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">02</div>
<div class="date-m">Jun</div>
<div class="date-y">2019</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>RICHARD M. LANGWORTH</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/current-contentions/" title="Read more about Churchill Contentions: “The Invasion of the Idiots”">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="766" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/lb1940-5crop-766x300.jpg" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="contentions" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /><noscript><img width="766" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/lb1940-5crop-766x300.jpg" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="contentions" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">The Churchill Project is honored to be in the van of defenders of the truth, and Sir Winston’s good name. We welcome the growing number of allies.</div>

