<h2 class="post_list_item_title"><a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/thatchers-speech-to-congress/" title="View full">Margaret Thatcher’s Speech to Congress</a></h2>
<div class="post_list_meta_unit">
<div class="date-d">25</div>
<div class="date-m">Apr</div>
<div class="date-y">2016</div>
</div>
<div class="post_list_inner_content_unit post_list_inner_content_unit_left">
<div class="authorlooplist">By <span>The Margaret Thatcher Foundation</span></div>
<a href="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/thatchers-speech-to-congress/" title="Read more about Margaret Thatcher’s Speech to Congress">
<div class="post_list_featured_image">
<img width="770" height="300" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-lazy-type="image" data-lazy-src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/margaret-thatcher-congress-770x300.png" class="lazy lazy-hidden img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Margaret Thatcher in congress" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /><noscript><img width="770" height="300" src="https://winstonchurchill.hillsdale.edu/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/margaret-thatcher-congress-770x300.png" class="img-responsive wp-post-image" alt="Margaret Thatcher in congress" decoding="async" loading="lazy" /></noscript> </div>
</a>
<div class="post_list_item_excerpt">"Wars are not caused by the build-up of weapons. They are caused when an aggressor believes he can achieve his objectives at an acceptable price." - Margaret Thatcher</div>

<div class="post_list_cats">
<span class="post_list_cats_label">Posted in:</span>
